          </ul></div><div id="posts"><article class="post type-text" id="5241958541"><aside class="metadata not-custom-page"><a class="timestamp" href="lesson-108-urdu-consonants-part-1-be">May 6th, 2011</a><!--  
                               <a class="note-count" href="http://www.learning-hindi.com/post/5241958541/lesson-108-urdu-consonants-part-1-ب-be#notes">14 notes</a> --><a class="comment-count" href="lesson-108-urdu-consonants-part-1-be#disqus_thread"></a><script type="text/javascript">
